Renault’s Ghosn to Play Key Electric-Car Role, Besson Tells TV5

-- B y   F a b i o   B e n e d e t t i - V a l e n t i n i
-- 
2011-03-20T20:04:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-20/renault-s-ghosn-to-play-key-electric-car-role-besson-tells-tv5.html
  Renault SA (RNO)  Chief Executive Officer  Carlos Ghosn , who apologized publicly to three senior executives
wrongly accused of spying, has a key role in the alliance with
Nissan Motor Co. and in an electric-car program, French Industry
Minister Eric Besson told  TV5  in an interview.  Separately, Besson said he has no fears about a radioactive
cloud that could reach France from Japan’s crippled Fukushima
Dai-Ichi plant, according to transcripts e-mailed by TV5.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Fabio Benedetti-Valentini in Paris at 
 fabiobv@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editors responsible for this story:
Frank Connelly at   fconnelly@bloomberg.net ;
Edward Evans at   eevans3@bloomberg.net . 